::Bobertron::

    "As I said over the comm Magmatron has left the base in my hands," 
Bobertron said to the Destrocons. "I am launching an offensive strike against 
the Iron Fist. I see you are flyers, you will be very useful."
    Bobertron knew about the Destrocons, Magmatron had secretly scanned them. 
He knew their past, and he knew they formed Destructus. 
    "I wish for you to attack the Iron Fist separately, do not form 
Destructus until I give the order. I want to puncture a hole in the ship and 
then have Destructus go in and destroy as much as he can. The other 
Destrocons will do the same.
